{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/Online_co-op.png?t=1701606424\" /><br>Spend your in-game time with your friends!<br>The game supports an online co-op mode (up to 5 players).<br>There is also a proximity voice chat.<br>Help each other, split into roles, brew potions together!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/Game_features.png?t=1701606424\" /><br>The main goal of the game is to <strong>brew potions</strong> for your guests. There are two ways to sell your potions: active and passive.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Active selling</strong> - open a shop for a constant flow of guests for a given time and brew ordered potions. The success rate of completed orders will matter.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/Active.gif?t=1701606424\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Passive selling</strong> - no need to rush, brew any potions you want and put them on the sale shelf.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/Passive.gif?t=1701606424\" /><br>Choose the one that you like the most.<br><br><strong>Rivals</strong> are waiting for you. They sell potions, just like you. Get ready to interfere with each other!<br><br>Wander through the magical forest and <strong>collect ingredients</strong>. Brew potions from them or sell them to a trader!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/Trading.gif?t=1701606424\" /><br><br><strong>The Build Mode</strong> lets you arrange in your house everything the way you want!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2226750/extras/Build.gif?t=1701606424\" /><br><br>Get new <st